name: Olga Kurylenko
description:
Olga Kurylenko is an actress. She has been in movies such as Black Widow and James Bond Quantum of Solace.

Used a lot of reference images here, about 60. I probably didnt need to use that many but I think this turned out really well.

Let me know what you think and any suggestions on who to see next.

If you like my work and wanna show me buy me a coffee
